Creating the DAX measures. 14
Creating all the measures for this project:

To create all the measures for this project click on the red button  on the top to download the word doc . The word doc contains all the measures for this project. Download and save it and create all the measures required for the KPIs and Visuals in the dashboard.  You should have 44 measures created when you are done. 

First create a Measure Table where all the measures will be saved. 

  • Select the Enter data icon on the panel .
  • Rename the table to Measure Table on the Name: 

After downloading the word doc file, then create the measures following the instructions as stated. 

Here is an example on how to create your measures.

Also, while creating your measures watch out for these signs and format because most of the measures has different signs and format.


How to create measures in Power BI by curbal:

https://curbal.com/blog/glossary/sum-dax
